data.description: Welcome to your upgraded and move-in ready home! Completed in 2021 and located in the desirable South Gulf Cove community, this spacious residence offers the perfect opportunity to embrace the idyllic Florida lifestyle. With easy access to the breathtaking beauty of Boca Grande and the abundant beach and boating activities in the Charlotte Harbor area, no detail has been overlooked in creating a home that exceeds expectations.  Step inside this DR Horton Jaden model and discover a modern oasis that will surpass your every desire. Luxury tile and vinyl flooring sets the stage for elegance throughout, while Bahama shutters add a touch of coastal charm. The home is equipped with Smart Home features, ensuring that even the most tech-savvy buyer will be impressed by the modern amenities. The heart of the home lies in the open kitchen and dining area, where warm natural light pours in, offering gorgeous views of the surrounding natural beauty. Top-of-the-line Samsung appliances, including a refrigerator with iPad functionality, along with the Samsung washer and dryer, provide the perfect blend of modern convenience and style.  This beautiful home boasts a coveted split floor plan, ensuring privacy and tranquility. While officially designated as a 3-bedroom/2bath with a den, this home seamlessly allows you the flexibility to adapt the space to your needs. The expansive owner's suite beckons with its ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks, a large walk-in shower, and his and hers walk-in closets. From the open kitchen and dining room areas, step outside to a private oasis and relax, unwind, or entertain family and friends while enjoying the Florida sunshine on the spacious paver patio and a screened-in lanai. For the ultimate indulgence, a 7-person hot tub awaits, offering the perfect spot for relaxation and rejuvenation.  The option to purchase this home furnished, with its beautiful coastal decor, is negotiable, adding further convenience and appeal.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home your own. Schedule your private showing today to fully appreciate the charm, upgrades, and the convenient access to the natural splendor of Boca Grande and the Charlotte Harbor beach and boating activities.
